CTMR Test Class Processing Test Plan HYB: Script should pass in Morning Intra-day and Weekend runs
In addition to this script CTMR Checkout script and System Checkout should be run on a Test Class with Test Firm Users
After script is complete give CTMR Team TestEvents.html file for verification as is done with current CTMR Checkout
Note:In Properties.txt file MAINCLASSLIST should contain Test Classes ONLY (Reporting classes only)
Note:In Properties.txt file MAINCLASSLIST1 should contain Production Classes ONLY (Reporting classes only)
In Properties.txt MM1 and MM2 users must be Test Firm
In Properties.txt MM3 and MM4 users must be normal Production Firm
In Properties.txt BADUSER1 and BADUSER2 users must be Invalid Firm (Such as CBOO:938 etc.) Use BADFIRM1 and BADFIRM2 properties to set the invalid firm
In Properties.txt BADUSER3 and BADUSER4 users must be set to Firm 999. Use BADFIRM3 and BADFIRM4 properties to set the invalid firm
